{"tid":2274302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普落後怪選舉舞弊 CNN：如快被曬乾的胖烏龜「自知時日不多」","createTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T11:11:13.000Z","uid":51665,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"481013c6cdceb01fd3364b9949695856b78c944b","tid":2274302,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"面臨連任陷入困境，美國總統川普5日發表大選之夜自稱勝選後的首次談話。川普在17分鐘的講話中，在沒有明確證據下指控大選多處舞弊等陰謀論，遭7家主流美媒直接切斷直播講話，或向觀眾強調「川普沒證據」。美國有線電視新聞網主播古柏直嗆，現在的川普正如同被太陽曬乾卻翻身不過來的肥胖烏龜，「此時他才深知自己時日不多了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川普在17分鐘的講話中大提陰謀論，稱大選幕後有科技、商葉與媒體鉅亨在背後剝奪他的勝選，並稱計算中的郵寄選票是詐欺，但全篇發言都沒有提出具體證據，讓《ABC》、《CBS》與《MSNBC》等7家美媒直接切斷川普記者會直播，而CNN與《福斯新聞》雖然未立即喊卡，但在川普講話結束後，向觀眾強調他並未提出具體證據。<br />\n<br />\n就在川普記者會結束後，CNN主播古柏（Anderson Cooper）感嘆：「那位是美國總統，那位是全世界最有權力的人，如今我們看到他就像一個在大太陽下極力翻身、卻翻不過來的肥胖烏龜，此時才知道到自己時日不多了」。不過他也強調，川普不會接受敗選結果，要把每一人都拖下水，包括整個國家。<br />\n<br />\n古柏的看法也引起許多切斷川普直播的同業們贊同。NBC主播霍爾特（Lester Holt）表示，「我們必須中斷直播，總統說了一連串虛假聲明，包括出現選舉舞弊，但他都沒提證據」。MSNBC主播威廉姆斯（Brian Williams）也指出，「我們又身處在一個極不尋常的處境，不僅要中斷總統的講話，還要修正他的發言」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8919907/Americas-major-networks-including-ABC-NBC-MSNBC-cut-Trump-17-minute-tirade.html?ito=social-facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ZWXh8Gh89mXOORYM_KOjF70engfuqkHjFCorPCbQZqQYwwNfZzt8uxSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8919907%2FAmericas-major-networks-including-ABC-NBC-MSNBC-cut-Trump-17-minute-tirade.html%3Fito%3Dsocial-facebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR1ZWXh8Gh89mXOORYM_KOjF70engfuqkHjFCorPCbQZqQYwwNfZzt8uxSw&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=dc704d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8919907/Americas-major-networks-including-ABC-NBC-MSNBC-cut-Trump-17-minute-tirade.html?ito=social-facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ZWXh8Gh89mXOORYM_KOjF70engfuqkHjFCorPCbQZqQYwwNfZzt8uxSw</a>"},{"pid":"772a09954aa4a2d4ff3ed34b8bff60f2f9066f1d","tid":2274302,"uid":379586,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"美國嘅制度真係四處漏水，搖搖欲墜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf605eb7144a95826c4e03223540f24dcb3157f","tid":2274302,"uid":161726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個整件黑猩猩衫<br />\n白左：racist<br />\n<br />\n白左： Donald Trump 係肥烏龜"},{"pid":"14b8a580a4edc1ec307a5e5c378c779ec683ef61","tid":2274302,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38bea3dd43351e02695a01b6b9c96dccfec9ca6","tid":2274302,"uid":63909,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"當年通俄門你哋班仆街日屌夜屌<br />\n咁點呀<br />\n咪又係乜都查唔到<br />\n而家又話要實質證據<br />\n無撚恥"},{"pid":"4c03f9608d4687704c6825e49b958e3a215777a6","tid":2274302,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"呢啲說話一定唔撕裂美國社會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d020820835e1546b707b37a9583deccdb20cd3","tid":2274302,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"屍嗯嗯收皮啦"},{"pid":"ea954ee022e7712fb0e806e1d610403de98801e1","tid":2274302,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"772a09954aa4a2d4ff3ed34b8bff60f2f9066f1d","tid":2274302,"uid":379586,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"美國嘅制度真係四處漏水，搖搖欲墜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"白左：Republicans = Nazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dc590975c60e063d3f8a51af074cc4c4b